lines.text: 4am, you call to spit some fire out
that i would listen to you now?
it's nothing new so get in line with all the rest
you realize you're out of breath
hate me all you want, i'll be okay
you've got sadness twisted up with jealousy
to make them look like loyalty
what holding on can take away
if it's the past you love
then that's where you can stay
hate me all you want, i'll be okay
but when it's on your sleeve you wear it well
you'll always have this war inside yourself
hate me all you want, i'll be okay
